<statement>
<p>
The amount paid at the time of purchase is called what?</p>
<p><ol style="list-style-type:upper-alpha"><li>Loan amount</li> 
<li>Down payment</li> 
<li>Compounding amount</li> 
<li>Interest</li> 
<li>Principal</li> 
<li>Compounding period</li> 
<li>None of the above</li> 
</ol></p>


</statement>
<answer>
<p><ul><li>B: Down payment</li></ul></p>
</answer>

